## Architecture Checks

### Domain Layer Has No Framework Dependencies

```bash
grep -r "org.springframework" src/domain/ || echo "✅ OK"
grep -r "jakarta.persistence" src/domain/ || echo "✅ OK"
grep -r "@Entity" src/domain/ || echo "✅ OK"
```

### Dependency Direction Is Correct

```
adapter/in → domain (depends on interface)
domain ← adapter/out (implements interface)
config → domain, adapter/in, adapter/out
```
